All of that seems to bypass the point though.  No matter what was intended for TLC it is a PROBLEM.  TLC messes up quests and conflicts with Verants other anti-farming measures (LORE/NODROP/NORENT).  The fact that the problems with TLC exist on Luclin show that Verant is not capable/willing to consider it in their -new- developments.  If they can/will-not do that how can anyone think they will take the time to go back and -fix- the problems that already exist with TLC.  I may very well be wrong, but I see no reason to believe that Verant will take the time/effort needed to make TLC work well.<br>
<br>
That said I believe their is no alternative but to remove TLC entirely.  Just my opinion though.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
